**Kisan Vikas Patra (KVP)** is a government savings certificate that doubles your money over a fixed tenure at a guaranteed rate. The current KVP rate is 7.5% p.a. (Q1 FY 2026-27), which means your money doubles in approximately 115 months (9 years and 7 months). There is no maximum investment limit and it can be pledged as collateral for a loan.
